OL,3,CCheryl pays tribute to Liam Payne
OL,4,Cafter his death
OL,6,FGirls Aloud singer Cheryl has paid
OL,7,Ftribute to Liam Payne after his death,
OL,8,FITV News' Correspondent Dan Rivers
OL,9,Freports from Buenos Aires
OL,11,FGirls Aloud singer Cheryl said the
OL,12,Fdeath of former One Direction star
OL,13,FLiam Payne is "breaking my heart", as
OL,14,Fher seven year-old son Bear has to
OL,15,F"face the reality of never seeing his
OL,16,Ffather again", in a statement posted
OL,17,Fon Instagram.
