OL,3,CCheryl pays tribute to Liam Payne
OL,4,Cafter his death
OL,6,FDescribing Payne's death as an "earth-
OL,7,Fshattering event", she also hit out at
OL,8,F"abhorrent reports and media
OL,9,Fexploitation", adding that "it is
OL,10,Fbreaking my heart further that I
OL,11,Fcannot protect him from that in his
OL,12,Ffuture".
OL,14,FThe pair were in a relationship
OL,15,Fbetween 2016 and 2018, and Cheryl gave
OL,16,Fbirth to their son in 2017.
OL,18,FPayne's father arrived at the hotel
OL,19,Fwhere his son had been staying to
OL,20,Fcollect his belongings.
