OL,3,CCheryl pays tribute to Liam Payne
OL,4,Cafter his death
OL,6,FHis father is the first family member
OL,7,Fto be seen in public since the
OL,8,Fsinger's death, having arrived in
OL,9,FBuenos Aires to arrange for the return
OL,10,Fof his son's body to England.
OL,12,FCheryl's full statement read: "As I
OL,13,Ftry to navigate this earth shattering
OL,14,Fevent, and work through my own grief
OL,15,Fat this indescribably painful time,
OL,16,FI'd like to kindly remind everyone
OL,17,Fthat we have lost a human being.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
