OL,3,CCheryl pays tribute to Liam Payne
OL,4,Cafter his death
OL,6,F"Liam was not only a pop star and
OL,7,Fcelebrity, he was a son, a brother, an
OL,8,Funcle, a dear friend and a father to
OL,9,Four seven-year-old son. A son that now
OL,10,Fhas to face the reality of never
OL,11,Fseeing his father again."
OL,13,FCheryl continued: "What is troubling
OL,14,Fmy spirit the most is that one day
OL,15,FBear will have access to the abhorrent
OL,16,Freports and media exploitation we have
OL,17,Fseen in the past two days. It is
OL,18,Fbreaking my heart further that I
OL,19,Fcannot protect him from that in his
OL,20,Ffuture.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
