OL,3,CCheryl pays tribute to Liam Payne
OL,4,Cafter his death
OL,6,F"I am begging you to consider what use
OL,7,Fsome of these reports are serving,
OL,8,Fother than to cause further harm to
OL,9,Feveryone left behind picking up the
OL,10,Fpieces. Before you leave comments or
OL,11,Fmake videos, ask yourself if you would
OL,12,Flike your own child or family to read
OL,13,Fthem.
OL,15,F"Please give Liam the little dignity
OL,16,Fhe has left in the wake of his death
OL,17,Fto rest in some peace at last. Thank
OL,18,Fyou, Cheryl."
