OL,3,CCheryl pays tribute to Liam Payne
OL,4,Cafter his death
OL,6,FThe pair initially met while Cheryl
OL,7,Fwas a judge on X Factor and Payne
OL,8,Fdebuted as a contestant. They began
OL,9,Ftheir relationship some eight years
OL,10,Flater.
OL,12,FHer tribute to Payne comes after One
OL,13,FDirection members posted a joint
OL,14,Fstatement, saying they are "completely
OL,15,Fdevastated" by the loss of their
OL,16,F"brother". It was the first post on
OL,17,Fthe band's Instagram account in four
OL,18,Fyears.
