OL,3,CCheryl pays tribute to Liam Payne
OL,4,Cafter his death
OL,6,FIn a separate statement, Louis
OL,7,FTomlinson, 32, wrote that Payne was
OL,8,F"the most vital part of One Direction"
OL,9,Fand added that he would be telling his
OL,10,Fyoung son Bear "stories of how amazing
OL,11,Fhis dad was".
OL,13,FZayn Malik said he never got to thank
OL,14,Fhim for supporting him through "some
OL,15,Fof the most difficult times", and that
OL,16,Fhe respected Payne, despite "butting
OL,17,Fheads" a few times.
