OL,6,FWhile Harry Styles said "Liam lived
OL,7,Fwide open, with his heart on his
OL,8,Fsleeve", and the years they spent
OL,9,Ftogether will remain "the most
OL,10,Fcherished" of his life. Niall Horan
OL,11,Fsaid he is "absolutely devastated" at
OL,12,Fthe loss of his "amazing friend".
OL,14,FFormer X Factor judge Simon Cowell
OL,15,Fsaid that he was "devastated" and that
OL,16,F"every tear I have shed is in memory
OL,17,Fof you".
